#: ../../../doc/en/changelog.rst:1155
msgid ""
"`#12544 <https://github.com/pytest-dev/pytest/issues/12544>`_, `#12545 "
"<https://github.com/pytest-dev/pytest/issues/12545>`_: Python virtual "
"environment detection was improved by checking for a :file:`pyvenv.cfg` "
