"``exc``."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/changelog.rst:1228
msgid ""
"``SetupState.stack`` failures are now a tuple ``(exc, tb)`` instead of "
"``exc``."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/changelog.rst:1232
msgid ""
"`#12275 <https://github.com/pytest-dev/pytest/issues/12275>`_: Fixed "
"collection error upon encountering an :mod:`abstract <abc>` class, including "
"abstract `unittest.TestCase` subclasses."
