#: ../../../doc/en/changelog.rst:1238
msgid ""
"`#12424 <https://github.com/pytest-dev/pytest/issues/12424>`_: Fixed crash "
"with `assert testcase is not None` assertion failure when re-running "
"unittest tests using plugins like pytest-rerunfailures. Regressed in 8.2.2."
