#: ../../../doc/en/changelog.rst:3520
msgid ""
":issue:`7527`: When a comparison between :func:`namedtuple <collections."
"namedtuple>` instances of the same type fails, pytest now shows the "
"differing field names (possibly nested) instead of their indexes."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/changelog.rst:3523
msgid ""
":issue:`7615`: :meth:`Node.warn <_pytest.nodes.Node.warn>` now permits any "
"subclass of :class:`Warning`, not just :class:`PytestWarning <pytest."
"PytestWarning>`."
