#: ../../../doc/en/changelog.rst:4464
msgid ""
":issue:`6469`: New options have been added to the :confval:`junit_logging` "
"option: ``log``, ``out-err``, and ``all``."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/changelog.rst:4467
msgid ""
":issue:`6834`: Excess warning summaries are now collapsed per file to ensure "
"readable display of warning summaries."
