"``faulthandler_timeout`` defined in the configuration file."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/changelog.rst:4566
msgid ""
":issue:`6597`: Fix node ids which contain a parametrized empty-string "
"variable."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/changelog.rst:4569
msgid ""
":issue:`6646`: Assertion rewriting hooks are (re)stored for the current "
