msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/changelog.rst:7309
msgid ""
":issue:`3610`: New ``--trace`` option to enter the debugger at the start of "
"a test."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/changelog.rst:7312
msgid ""
":issue:`3623`: Introduce ``pytester.copy_example`` as helper to do "
"acceptance tests against examples from the project."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/changelog.rst:7319
msgid ""
":issue:`2220`: Fix a bug where fixtures overridden by direct parameters (for "
"example parametrization) were being instantiated even if they were not being "
