"Fix ``usefixtures`` mark applied to unittest tests by correctly "
"instantiating ``FixtureInfo``. (:issue:`3498`)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/changelog.rst:7460
msgid ""
"Fix assertion rewriter compatibility with libraries that monkey patch "
