#: ../../../doc/en/changelog.rst:9307
msgid ""
"**Important**: `py.code <https://pylib.readthedocs.io/en/stable/code.html>`_ "
"has been merged into the ``pytest`` repository as ``pytest._code``. This "
"decision was made because ``py.code`` had very few uses outside ``pytest`` "
"and the fact that it was in a different repository made it difficult to fix "
"bugs on its code in a timely manner. The team hopes with this to be able to "
"better refactor out and improve that code. This change shouldn't affect "
"users, but it is useful to let users aware if they encounter any strange "
"behavior."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/changelog.rst:9316
